title: HOUR 3- Peter King Oct 01, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Peter King Oct 01, 2020
description:
Peter King tells Dan that the NFL did not want to pull the plug for the Titans game and that they really wanted to play the game on Monday late afternoon. Peter says that this probably wont be the only game that gets adjusted this year.
